Package: IRRsim
Title: Simulate Inter-Rater Reliability Statistics
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2018-02-06
Authors@R: 
    person("Jason", "Bryer", , "jason@bryer.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Functions and shiny application to simulate inter-rater
    reliability statistics based on various scoring and response models.
    The initial motivation for this package is to understand the
    relationship between percent rater agreement and intraclass
    correlation.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: http://irrsim.bryer.org, http://github.com/jbryer/IRRsim
BugReports: https://github.com/jbryer/IRRsim/issues
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5.0)
